Title: The Solar System – An Overview
Slide 1: Introduction

The Solar System consists of the Sun and everything that orbits around it, including planets, moons, comets, and asteroids.

Slide 2: The Planets

There are 8 planets in our solar system:

Mercury

Venus

Earth

Mars

Jupiter

Saturn

Uranus

Neptune

Slide 3: Fun Fact – The Sun

The Sun is a star at the center of our solar system.
It is made mostly of hydrogen and helium.

